# --- Optional: Arduino ESP32 over HTTP ---
# If unset, the dashboard uses the built-in mock voltage stream.
#
# Development (same Wi‑Fi as your PC): use the Vite proxy so the browser
# does not need CORS on the chip. Point DEV_ESP32_TARGET at the ESP32 IP.
#
# VITE_ESP32_VOLTAGE_URL=/esp32-proxy/voltage
# DEV_ESP32_TARGET=http://192.168.1.50
#
# Production / LAN without proxy: call the board directly (chip must send
# Access-Control-Allow-Origin — see firmware sketch).
#
# VITE_ESP32_VOLTAGE_URL=http://192.168.1.50/voltage
